summary: So do you think it's entirely possible that Taylor's dress at the Billboard awards was planned that far in advance that it could...
body:
Ts7 theory no.193738

So do you think it’s entirely possible that Taylor’s dress at the Billboard awards was planned that far in advance that it could have been when she was still planning or going ahead with the 🌴 era before she realised she had to release reputation?

The dress seems to be a very similar aesthetic to what she’s currently posting and I was shocked when I saw her in that dress, I was expecting something a lot more metallic and maybe snake skin styled.

Also she wrote Babe when she was writing Red, but it wasn’t released until rep was out - perhaps she decided to go ahead to Sugarland again when she was planning Ts6 to be 🌴 era. It’s country and goes back to her roots that wouldn’t have suited a more etherial and love song style era.

It would also explain her Spotify Singles.

Perhaps she always wanted them to be stripped back acoustics with a country twist but when the time got round to recording them Ts6 had already switched from 🌴 to 🐍.
